name: Goldilocks And The Three Bears (Urooj.Mubashir)
description:
Goldilocks and the Three Bears, Is an educational fairytale story.

This Story is about the three bears and a girl known as Goldilocks, In this story, we will get to know that how Goldilocks interfere with someone else privacy.

  The most interesting thing about this story is that how beautifully the main theme and the concept of the story is represented, that you should consider the consequences of your actions
